This project is a fully responsive and modern e-commerce website built using React, JavaScript, Framer Motion, Tailwind CSS, and more. Designed with a sleek purple-themed UI, it showcases Apple products in a clean and interactive shopping experience.

✨ Key Features:
🖥️ Product Showcase – Explore a range of Apple products with elegant product cards and images

🧾 Filter & Sort Options – Users can filter products by categories, price, and features

💬 User Reviews – Dynamic review sections for product credibility

🎨 Framer Motion Animations – Smooth transitions and UI animations for a futuristic feel

📱 Responsive Design – Mobile-first layout with Tailwind’s utility classes

⚙️ Component-Based Architecture – Clean React component structure for scalability
